# 📘 Linear Control Teaching Assistant Series - Chapter 1

[![Telegram Channel](https://img.shields.io/badge/Telegram-Channel-blue?style=for-the-badge&logo=telegram)](https://t.me/+zv9wk3xFmco3NTQ0)
[![Google Drive Resources](https://img.shields.io/badge/Resources-Google%20Drive-orange?style=for-the-badge&logo=googledrive)](https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1YFUMgs5hpfA0IkPIXaQlTO1O-hVTTjXz?usp=drive_link)

Welcome to the Linear Control teaching assistant series. This series provides a structured walkthrough of core topics in linear control, from modeling to state-space representation. Each session covers essential concepts and offers practical examples for better understanding.

## 📹 Video Sessions

### Session 1: MATLAB Introduction Series
- **Overview**: Comprehensive introduction to MATLAB for control system applications.
📌 [Watch on Telegram](https://t.me/c/2152409151/17)

### Session 2: Chapter 1, Part 1
- **Topics**:
  - Modeling
  - DC Motor
  - Transfer Function
  - Block Diagrams
  - Simplification of Block Diagrams
📌 [Watch on Google Drive](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1H-m-pivApYQPAj9jBPF_wrNRUIGPLiv7/view?usp=drive_link)

### Session 3: Chapter 1, Part 2
- **Topics**:
  - Laplace Transform
  - Signal Flow Graphs
  - Mason’s Gain Formula
  - State Space Representation
📌 [Watch on Google Drive](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1_NAO7OrdGPtkznTcIb0ZfZIvD_3TP6jM/view?usp=drive_link)

